=head1 NAME

S400RACD - Performs an Oracle Database Hang Analysis

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This module performs an Oracle database hang analysis.

The following reports can be generated and are regrouped under C<Hang Analysis>
in C<Cluster>:

=cut

echo tput('bold'),'Performing a hang analysis ...',tput('off')

# Initialization
var $DATABASE_INSTALLED = getSetting('DATABASE_INSTALLED')

var $TOC = '%TOC%'
var $TOP = '[[#Top][Back to top]]'
toc '^1:Cluster'
toc '1+:Hang Analysis'

=head2 diag - Diagnostics

Runs diagnostic scripts in the database.

=cut

debug ' Inside RACD module, running diagnostic scripts in the database'
if $DATABASE_INSTALLED
 run RACdiag()

# Disable the group title in next index
toc '-:Cluster'

